*giggles*
Poor Minkin :)

Halana, shaman
Tani, bard
Solusekro

>
>
> Well i topped off my bad looks yesterday... I'm a wood elf with:
>
> ss helm
> ss gloves
> ss boots
> hero bracer ... Not too bad right? lotsa green.
>
> My other stuff includes:
> lambent bracer
> lambent legs
> lambent arms.. add in the blue
>
> tree weave
> mith bp
> worn cloth mantle
> guise of deceiver
> rune bone fork
> troll hide belt
> 2 yaks
> mm drum & nos tamborine
> gypsie princess lute
>
> various jewelry
>
> Well last night i topped off my ugly look by replacing my
> lambent bracer for
> a Kylong Wrist guard (same stats but more charisma). THE
> BRACER IS BROWNISH
> RED!! i freaked out when i saw it, it keeps overwriting my
> hero bracer
> look. I never though i could look worse but oh boy when i put
> that on did i
> ever freak.
>
> While i'm auctioning, some twink bard in full lambent at lev
> 12 pops up to
> me asks me what i wanted for my hero bracer (im auctioning it
> because i have
> a spare) then after a wee bit says oh nm, i thought you were
> a twink and
> not a real player. Talk about kicking me while im down.
>
> Sooo anyways, that kicked me in the butt severely and now im really
> determined to powerlevel instead of grouping (which i would
> much rather do).
> I have to kiss my lambent and tree weave goodbye soon and get
> some imbrued,
> im tired of looking like all the twinks with various ss and
> lambent. Dont
> get me wrong, i have nothing against twinking but man im sick
> of passing for
> something that is 20-30 levels lower then i really am.
>
> Arg sorry for the rant
>
> Minkin
> almost lev 42 bard
> The Menace of Rathe Mountains
> Sol ro

> I am bard, hear me sing!
